Second Department,

July, 1974

(July 19, 1974)* The People of the State of New York ex rel. Leslie Green, Petitioner, v. Superintendent, Green Haven Correctional Facility, Respondent.

Not published with other decisions of July, 1974, 45 A D 2d 838. [Rep.

Application by petitioner for a writ of habeas corpus denied. Gulotta, P. J., Hopkins', Martusceljo, Latham and Shapiro, JJ., concur.
